      <sec id="Sec7">
        <title>Negative binomial distribution</title>
        <p id="Par18">A negative binomial distribution, which arises from a Gamma-Poisson mixture, can be parameterized as follows [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR35">35</xref>â<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR37">37</xref>] (see â<xref rid="Sec19" ref-type="sec">Methods</xref>â for derivation).</p>
