      <p id="Par68">The expected basal transcription, <italic>E</italic>(<italic>Ï</italic><sub><italic>i</italic></sub>), becomes the mean incidence rate of <italic>y</italic><sub><italic>i</italic></sub> per unit of exposure, <italic>t</italic><sub><italic>i</italic></sub>.</p>
